,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T10:34:11.000Z","msg":"咪撚貼hk01"},{"pid":"a975417c71263c42adee52056bd9ed2016570de6","tid":1687973,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"中國零一又嚟料"},{"pid":"385b89e8c04a918814132a80e510a669c20ecf1c","tid":1687973,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T10:46:51.000Z","msg":"佢地day1已經有槍，上頭一早預左要開槍架啦"},{"pid":"111d0f2a5dedc4f97288261e490b5b21f70d810f","tid":1687973,"uid":204227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T10:49:59.000Z","msg":"警方曾多次開真槍，更曾打中示威者胸部，但無人因為中槍死<br />\n<br />\n係咪直接認咗有示威者唔係因為中槍而死"},{"pid":"57e296b35e0cf05ba8e45f89590715cb0d4f474a","tid":1687973,"uid":114822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"218906091874f8a1098025e478c96a281639fc9a","tid":1687973,"uid":200495,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T08:24:07.000Z","msg":"Hk01 明哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T10:53:41.000Z","msg":"01啲賤種連字都唔識多隻學人報新聞<br />\n&ldquo;not that I would necessarily die&rdquo;竟然譯做「不那樣做我一定會死」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}